Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.06,0:00:03.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年打算怎么办  
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.42,0:00:08.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯  你要做点心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.29,0:00:10.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.23,0:00:12.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.83,0:00:14.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了情人节啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.24,0:00:15.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.76,0:00:16.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要给谁
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.21,0:00:18.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爵士研的学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.78,0:00:21.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年我想亲手做做看
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.31,0:00:24.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓打算怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.85,0:00:25.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.59,0:00:27.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不给轻音部的学姐吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.15,0:00:31.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…嗯  去年也没给呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.11,0:00:33.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.47,0:00:35.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本来是想给的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.30,0:00:36.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.68,0:00:38.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比利时皇室？！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.46,0:00:42.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我得到了那个叫作御用达的巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.46,0:00:43.84,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（ベルギー王室御用達（比利时皇室御用巧克力）：一种高档巧克力品牌认证，\N主要有Godiva、Wittamer、Galler、Neuhaus等品牌存在）  
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.07,0:00:43.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带来给大家吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.92,0:00:48.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为太好吃而忘了给她们
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.76,0:00:50.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好羡慕你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.49,0:00:51.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忧呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.58,0:00:54.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去年做得少
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.81,0:00:58.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只给了姐姐和隔壁的老奶奶  
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.36,0:00:59.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.51,0:01:00.72,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年我会带来给大家的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.97,0:01:02.64,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.96,0:01:01.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在回想一下  
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.52,0:01:04.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一次都没给过学姐们巧克力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.86,0:01:06.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  小梓
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.32,0:01:06.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.01,0:01:10.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我可没在想情人节的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.88,0:01:12.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不打自招  不打自招
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.15,0:02:52.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who？  
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.66,0:02:53.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.29,0:02:55.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.88,0:02:58.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到Who的话  当然就是基斯·穆恩所在的乐队了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.10,0:02:59.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样的吗  
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.24,0:03:02.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这里不是那个意思  
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.37,0:03:06.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个大概是关系代词的Who吧  
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.93,0:03:09.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和这部分关联在一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.27,0:03:10.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不明白～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.65,0:03:11.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是基础啊  
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.75,0:03:13.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  没关系的  小律
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.83,0:03:15.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了万不得已的时候还有那招  
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.96,0:03:17.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊哈  说得对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.64,0:03:18.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那招是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.82,0:03:21.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,选择题用答卷纸就交给这个了  
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.69,0:03:23.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六角形君「7号」  
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.59,0:03:24.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.68,0:03:25.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.96,0:03:28.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用各种铅笔尝试后得出的结论…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.24,0:03:32.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,7号可是创下了正确率60%记录的佳品
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.80,0:03:35.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如说  这个问题的答案是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.21,0:03:37.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's answer three
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.52,0:03:39.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,答对了  
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.46,0:03:40.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,YES！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.07,0:03:43.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有了这个就一定能合格了  
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.88,0:03:44.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.59,0:03:49.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次考试的选择题可是有九个备选的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.37,0:03:50.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一定不及格了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.91,0:03:51.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放弃得好快…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.59,0:03:54.74,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不行了  等着吃零蛋吧～ 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.11,0:03:57.96,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别放弃  首先先记住语法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.05,0:03:54.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巧克力吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.44,0:03:56.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但觉得好难为情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.45,0:03:58.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,郑重其事地给她们也有点…  
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.64,0:03:59.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小梓？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.55,0:04:00.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.34,0:04:01.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了  
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.37,0:04:03.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不  没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.61,0:04:07.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓  你不用顾虑我们  可以一个人练习啊  
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.84,0:04:08.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  没错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.87,0:04:10.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,BGM  请  
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.45,0:04:11.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,YES～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.23,0:04:13.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…那么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.07,0:04:22.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦～弹得很不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.50,0:04:23.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.38,0:04:25.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  我们继续学习
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.43,0:04:26.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.37,0:04:38.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.01,0:04:40.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.22,0:04:43.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微休息一下？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.95,0:04:45.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去泡点茶喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.28,0:04:46.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.53,0:04:49.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经忍不住了  稍微去碰一下鼓
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.55,0:04:50.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.94,0:04:53.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…在那之前得先去厕所
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.76,0:04:55.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小梓也来喝杯茶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.57,0:04:56.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.08,0:04:57.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.27,0:05:01.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好像打扰到学姐们学习了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.32,0:05:05.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  本来就是我们用活动室来学习的不对  
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.15,0:05:11.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我反而是有音乐更能集中呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.48,0:05:13.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以尽量弹哦  
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.68,0:05:18.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小梓  你要喝奶茶吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.94,0:05:19.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.20,0:05:23.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  我只准备了曲奇饼干…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.62,0:05:25.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会  已经足够了  
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.63,0:05:27.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学习比较重要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.30,0:05:33.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实因为马上就要到情人节了  所以想准备一些巧克力的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.94,0:05:39.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯～那今年小梓也给学姐们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.19,0:05:44.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  好像学姐也没有准备巧克力的慰劳品  
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.69,0:05:48.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得给学姐们一次也好  
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.68,0:05:49.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  嗯  
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.79,0:05:52.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊  小梓亲手做的巧克力  
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.64,0:05:53.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也会给忧的  
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.10,0:05:54.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.10,0:05:56.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我也会带来给你的  
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.98,0:05:57.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.77,0:06:00.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊  小梓亲手做的巧克力  
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.45,0:06:02.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了  纯也给  
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.31,0:06:02.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.13,0:06:04.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.80,0:06:09.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不能告诉唯学姐她们！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.20,0:06:10.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.68,0:06:11.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯也是  
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.78,0:06:13.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.32,0:06:14.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.17,0:06:17.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像已经让很多人知道了  
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.84,0:06:19.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小梓  加油
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.92,0:06:21.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小梓  好可爱  
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.75,0:06:24.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟…糟了！  
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.58,0:06:35.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.17,0:06:38.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到考试当天会下雪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.80,0:06:41.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准考证  准考证在这里面
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.82,0:06:43.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这个口袋里面  
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.04,0:06:45.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还真费心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.78,0:06:47.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小律没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.41,0:06:48.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了  
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.75,0:06:51.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天确实放进这里了…  
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.41,0:06:52.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.67,0:06:54.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.81,0:06:57.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  难道是…那个？  
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.10,0:07:00.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好险
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.34,0:07:01.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  别这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.81,0:07:03.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.50,0:07:06.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.75,0:07:07.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小唯  早上好  
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.04,0:07:08.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.16,0:07:11.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别…别和我说话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.93,0:07:17.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,单词会从脑袋里漏…漏出来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.44,0:07:18.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.66,0:07:20.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有…有什么漏出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.39,0:07:23.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么漏出来了  
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.05,0:07:25.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终极临时抱佛脚啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.42,0:07:26.00,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么  什么漏出来了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.29,0:07:38.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考试已经开始了吧  
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.87,0:07:40.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.97,0:07:42.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  纯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.63,0:07:45.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓也在为情人节买东西？  
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.93,0:07:46.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.93,0:07:48.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备做什么  
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.18,0:07:49.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想做巧克力蛋糕  
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.98,0:07:51.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是看了书之后觉得有点难做
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.53,0:07:54.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来看看  材料要哪些？  
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.63,0:07:59.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,细砂糖和生奶油
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.55,0:08:03.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  砂糖不是就在这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.05,0:08:05.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真的呢  
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.69,0:08:07.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说…那是黑砂糖
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.03,0:08:10.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巧克力也是黑的  不是正好吗  
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.81,0:08:12.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.78,0:08:16.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巧克力的话  那边有个不错的  
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.48,0:08:19.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,制作点心用的板状巧克力？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.54,0:08:20.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巧克力就是巧克力啊  
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.18,0:08:22.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不都一样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.65,0:08:26.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…接下来是…  
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.90,0:08:27.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯  
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.81,0:08:28.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.01,0:08:30.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有好好做过吗  
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.23,0:08:32.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了  
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.86,0:08:34.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗  
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.53,0:08:36.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  小梓  小纯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.23,0:08:38.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  忧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.57,0:08:41.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么  忧也在为情人节买东西？  
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.21,0:08:41.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.26,0:08:44.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是几人份的？  
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.84,0:08:45.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.58,0:08:47.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…总之这是姐姐的那份吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.47,0:08:49.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是一人份？！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.83,0:08:50.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.89,0:08:52.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小梓要做什么  
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.46,0:08:55.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是想做巧克力蛋糕的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.28,0:08:59.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们一起做吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.82,0:09:00.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.62,0:09:01.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…  
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.29,0:09:02.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.61,0:09:04.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你刚才的强硬态度跑哪里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.49,0:09:07.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐呐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.67,0:09:09.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有一双软软的拖鞋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.00,0:09:10.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们要哪个？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.11,0:09:12.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.07,0:09:16.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分量要秤准确  
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.55,0:09:17.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.76,0:09:19.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小纯  巧克力融化了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.29,0:09:21.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.54,0:09:23.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好甜～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.60,0:09:25.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在舔可不行啊  
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.74,0:09:27.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样行了吧  
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.82,0:09:28.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不  
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.64,0:09:29.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀呵～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.97,0:09:31.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯…唯学姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.68,0:09:33.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不是时候  
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.68,0:09:33.77,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  姐姐  回来得好早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.89,0:09:35.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  因为只考两科  
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.10,0:09:38.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓喵你们来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.30,0:09:39.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎…啊  是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.91,0:09:42.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不能被她发现
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.66,0:09:44.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考…考得怎么样  
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.06,0:09:45.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.38,0:09:51.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道  
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.46,0:09:52.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.56,0:09:53.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在做什么  
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.70,0:09:57.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像闻到了巧克力的香味  
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.70,0:09:59.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.31,0:10:00.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在做巧克力蛋糕哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.67,0:10:01.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说出来了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.12,0:10:03.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.35,0:10:05.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好了让我吃一点  
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.51,0:10:06.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了  知道了  
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.97,0:10:08.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要说出来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.51,0:10:12.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都在做点心  她不会想到是为了情人节的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.68,0:10:13.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.23,0:10:18.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  用来装饰的粉末砂糖没有了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.04,0:10:20.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.78,0:10:22.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,附近就有卖的  我去买  
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.71,0:10:25.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那么我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.61,0:10:28.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…留在家里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.75,0:10:29.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是留下来？  
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.33,0:10:33.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  烧好了就从烤箱倒出来  
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.32,0:10:34.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了  
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.98,0:10:36.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.84,0:10:38.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯肯定会偷尝味道什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.80,0:10:41.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  稍等一下  
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.19,0:10:41.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.17,0:10:43.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百度参？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.17,0:10:43.52,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（指在同一家神社参拜一百次）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.71,0:10:47.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  就在家旁边嘛  所以每次路过我都会扔10日元进去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.35,0:10:50.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多有100次了吧  
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.50,0:10:51.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真随意啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.53,0:10:59.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,许了什么愿？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.06,0:11:07.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望姐姐她们能全员考入同一所大学并顺利毕业
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.83,0:11:11.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  那么我也来  
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.78,0:11:16.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.16,0:11:21.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,K-ON!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.38,0:11:28.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…感觉好紧张
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.60,0:11:29.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我送过了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.66,0:11:31.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.91,0:11:32.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很完美
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.85,0:11:33.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.72,0:11:36.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轻音部的学姐们还没来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.32,0:11:40.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  但是在这里送给她们真的合适吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.91,0:11:42.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉很难为情…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.95,0:11:44.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难为情？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.03,0:11:47.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学姐！这  这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.19,0:11:48.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然会有些苦…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.23,0:11:51.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但其中包含着我无比甜蜜的心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.16,0:11:53.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢…谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.56,0:11:57.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此  的确很难为情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.22,0:11:58.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…我才不会说那种话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.93,0:12:02.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那偷偷放进吉他盒里怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.48,0:12:04.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候放是个问题…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.31,0:12:06.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.12,0:12:09.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险！队长  是炸弹！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.67,0:12:11.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能会引起骚动呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.07,0:12:13.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…不会的  不会的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.41,0:12:16.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  普通的放在课桌里怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.06,0:12:19.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢  这样的话还行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.42,0:12:20.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.24,0:12:21.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,律  先走了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.96,0:12:24.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  稍微等一下啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.57,0:12:26.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.33,0:12:28.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,微妙地很有可能发生…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.16,0:12:32.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎～绝对是黑芝麻味布丁啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.38,0:12:34.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  有那种的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.49,0:12:36.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  很好吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.99,0:12:38.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉得什么比较好？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.64,0:12:40.44,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我果然还是喜欢油梨味的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.72,0:12:41.82,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.13,0:12:40.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.34,0:12:41.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.30,0:12:43.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋山学姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.15,0:12:46.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  请收下这个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.41,0:12:48.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  谢…谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.33,0:12:50.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.69,0:12:52.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是传说中的演唱会的主唱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.49,0:12:54.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烦死了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.19,0:12:55.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别害羞嘛～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.72,0:12:56.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.58,0:12:58.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.05,0:13:01.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没有送出去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.03,0:13:04.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  都已经到午休时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.83,0:13:07.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  放学后再送也可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.95,0:13:08.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.18,0:13:12.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澪学姐一定会收到像山一样多的巧克力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.41,0:13:14.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果和大家一起吃了可怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.26,0:13:17.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放学后巧克力都吃饱了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.89,0:13:20.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会一次性吃那么多巧克力的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.87,0:13:22.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想说先下手为强
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.26,0:13:24.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.69,0:13:26.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一定会很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.01,0:13:28.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.37,0:13:30.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也去送送看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.06,0:13:32.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  给谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.70,0:13:33.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澪学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.78,0:13:35.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可是我憧憬的贝司手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.03,0:13:37.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  那…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.43,0:13:39.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  轻音部的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.03,0:13:41.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真的诶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.54,0:13:43.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澪她们的话在办公室里哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.57,0:13:45.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非…非常感谢！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.88,0:13:47.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好紧张～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.50,0:13:49.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的样子被记住了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.16,0:13:50.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.68,0:13:53.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.94,0:13:54.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.30,0:13:58.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小唯和小律的第三志愿合格
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.00,0:14:02.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小澪和小第二志愿也合格了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.70,0:14:05.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过还真是一如既往的大赛型呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.13,0:14:06.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,V！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.06,0:14:08.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可不是在夸你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.12,0:14:11.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还剩下大家一起的第一志愿呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.51,0:14:13.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候公布？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.37,0:14:15.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后天
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.54,0:14:16.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.54,0:14:18.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你们一起考进哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.31,0:14:20.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.26,0:14:23.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此考试也全结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.30,0:14:27.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到毕业前就把之前努力的时间休息回来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.25,0:14:28.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.13,0:14:29.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕业吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.29,0:14:29.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.89,0:14:31.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.40,0:14:32.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  是小梓啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.51,0:14:34.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀呵～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.79,0:14:36.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  有什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.24,0:14:38.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  实际上…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.26,0:14:40.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  梓
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.56,0:14:45.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个…这个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.35,0:14:45.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.22,0:14:47.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请收下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.92,0:14:49.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢…谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.49,0:14:52.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  还有学姐们的  给
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.24,0:14:52.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.06,0:14:54.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…啊  好小
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.42,0:14:55.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是很可爱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.83,0:14:58.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  梓也…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.30,0:14:59.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.62,0:15:02.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎～梓也带过来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.75,0:15:04.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓喵巧克力？好想吃！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.53,0:15:07.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.39,0:15:14.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  我稍微去下洗手间…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.30,0:15:15.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.22,0:15:17.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等一下  梓？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.87,0:15:18.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.18,0:15:20.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青春啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.60,0:15:22.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.98,0:15:24.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.85,0:15:27.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.83,0:15:29.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.33,0:15:32.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是这么害羞的事情啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.09,0:15:34.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这么普通的送出去就好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.97,0:15:35.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说句「给」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.99,0:15:37.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.19,0:15:37.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.65,0:15:40.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这样的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.76,0:15:45.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家就要毕业了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.82,0:15:49.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家就要这么离开了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.87,0:15:55.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.80,0:16:12.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  我去社团活动了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.14,0:16:15.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说好今天学姐她们都会过来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.66,0:16:17.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.54,0:16:18.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.37,0:16:22.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小梓…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.25,0:16:22.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.76,0:16:26.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定得把巧克力送掉哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.42,0:16:29.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.43,0:16:31.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  加油  小梓
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.99,0:16:32.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.90,0:16:33.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.21,0:16:35.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.73,0:16:40.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.33,0:16:42.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.40,0:16:42.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.55,0:16:46.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯…唯学姐？不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.04,0:16:48.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说  你在这边做什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.21,0:16:51.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为感觉到了梓喵的气息…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.67,0:16:52.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这算什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.01,0:16:54.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  梓！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.71,0:16:58.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天可是珍藏的茶哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.84,0:17:00.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.94,0:17:02.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确很香啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.09,0:17:04.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  说起来…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.79,0:17:05.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的点心呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.98,0:17:08.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  今天没有准备
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.93,0:17:12.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相反啊  小梓好像准备了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.77,0:17:15.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  怎…怎么会露馅的？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.67,0:17:21.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小佐和说了「记得把我的那份留下来哦」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.31,0:17:26.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.39,0:17:27.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓喵是天才！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.86,0:17:29.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没那么夸张啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.70,0:17:31.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  真的很好吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.67,0:17:33.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.51,0:17:36.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说梓  巧克力蛋糕果然就是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.17,0:17:39.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？  呃…该怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.87,0:17:42.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作…作为平时的感谢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.46,0:17:44.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此  感谢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.40,0:17:46.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  作为回礼请收下这个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.29,0:17:49.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.48,0:17:50.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糖酱啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.62,0:17:52.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白色情人节的回礼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.35,0:17:52.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好早！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.99,0:17:53.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好便宜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.89,0:17:56.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在白色情人节当天回礼就没意义了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.57,0:17:58.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.81,0:18:00.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢款待～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.22,0:18:02.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢品尝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.06,0:18:05.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小佐和早点过来就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.87,0:18:07.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.62,0:18:08.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.71,0:18:09.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.59,0:18:10.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.42,0:18:11.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下得好大哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.13,0:18:13.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.11,0:18:16.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  已经是雪白一片啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.46,0:18:18.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎～我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.44,0:18:20.87,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  那辆卡车都积满雪了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.04,0:18:21.80,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.14,0:18:22.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我也想看！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.35,0:18:26.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.40,0:18:28.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊  全都来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.43,0:18:32.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等  等一下  别丢下我啦～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.22,0:18:34.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好  快过来啦～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.53,0:18:36.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔…看不见
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.64,0:18:40.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  别硬挤啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.33,0:18:41.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼唧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.39,0:18:43.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  小孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.35,0:18:45.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  雪白一片！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.56,0:18:46.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真漂亮啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.91,0:18:48.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年下得真大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.14,0:18:51.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.19,0:18:53.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇～那孩子真是危险啊  
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.60,0:18:54.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.98,0:18:56.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乐福便鞋很容易在雪地上滑倒…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.60,0:18:57.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  这是禁句！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.11,0:19:00.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  抱歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.42,0:19:12.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.18,0:19:12.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.06,0:19:15.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和大家一起感觉真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.21,0:19:19.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然今天从早上开始就很冷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.79,0:19:23.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但和学姐们在一起  却一点都不觉得冷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.62,0:19:25.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  当然小猪也是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.26,0:19:29.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯学姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.78,0:19:30.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿嘿…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.39,0:19:34.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好温暖好温暖哦  梓喵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.42,0:19:36.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.50,0:19:38.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好温暖好温暖～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.95,0:19:41.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好温暖好温暖～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.64,0:19:45.51,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好温暖～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.59,0:19:45.77,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.97,0:19:46.72,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小佐和
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.31,0:19:55.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,10日元×100次！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.69,0:19:58.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.73,0:20:12.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望学姐们一定一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.25,0:20:16.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定一定一定一定一定一定一～定
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.63,0:20:20.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起第一志愿合格！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.95,0:20:29.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后  直到毕业大家都要笑着渡过
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.33,0:20:40.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.15,0:20:46.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯学姐给的糖…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.05,0:20:56.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好甜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.27,0:21:07.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上了  准备
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.14,0:21:10.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…喂  还只是练习而已吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.12,0:21:14.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那篇长文…  如果那篇长文没有错的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.79,0:21:17.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没注定就会落榜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.41,0:21:22.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是啊  就算考上不同的大学我们也还是好朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.63,0:21:24.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说  你倒是看了以后再说这话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.92,0:21:26.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,临阵脱逃的话就绝交哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.18,0:21:28.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.47,0:21:30.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  这次真上了哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.45,0:21:32.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.34,0:21:33.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.31,0:21:34.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定行的！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.68,0:21:35.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.68,0:21:36.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放学后茶会！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.23,0:21:38.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.12,0:21:34.93,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.67,0:21:37.69,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.13,0:21:39.22,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.09,0:21:41.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.13,0:21:46.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一  二…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.54,0:22:05.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.25,0:22:07.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了～！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.03,0:23:44.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天好暖和啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.67,0:23:46.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失礼咯…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.30,0:23:47.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…去哪里玩吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.41,0:23:49.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.24,0:23:51.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  玩什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.13,0:23:53.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来个大较量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.71,0:23:54.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.75,0:24:03.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是自己的教室  但感觉像不是似的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.07,0:24:04.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯


